strings: <voice_0x01000EFC><se_def>the prince carlos: No no! This method is not working! He wasn't old enough to impress my father or anyone else.
<voice_0x01000EFD><se_def>the prince carlos: I wish there were more chameleons! So let's take them on and see if we can hit the jackpot...
<voice_0x01000EFE><se_def>the prince carlos: But the chameleon in the wild saw me coming and ran away. I'm so scared all the time! interesting
<voice_0x01000EFF><se_high>Accuracy: This person is very happy with himself. How much time are you going to spend taking care of this little one?
<voice_0x01000F00><se_low>January: Who would have thought that a man would become king?
<voice_0x01000F01><se_def>China: Somebody has to get a hold of this kid's arrogance...
<voice_0x01000F02><se_def>the prince carlos: Anyway, now I'm hungry.
<voice_0x01000F03><se_def>the prince carlos: In earnest! Finished the day's work<:> Level the floor and spend the night.
The group spends the night in the mountains.
